{"tid":966032,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友瀨屎，分唔分手好？","createTime":"2019-01-02T13:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T16:31:07.000Z","uid":224862,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5abb42da76cdaed59d388ef933965ba022350b8c","tid":966032,"uid":224862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:22:40.000Z","msg":"今年21歳 男朋友24歳<br />\n平時又唔番工 仲要衰到問我借錢 <br />\n但係都唔緊要 因為始終係自己男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但最接受唔到係去台灣旅行個陣 佢竟然瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要好自然同我講佢瀨咗屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我幫佢買褲 又幫佢搵廁所<br />\n點知轉個頭發尻我脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見我唔出聲個陣又問我 佢係咪好失禮我 係到自己發老脾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ⋯"},{"pid":"6e7772f7e90c701d8b433971de8e0b938f633fc6","tid":966032,"uid":194076,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:24:08.000Z","msg":"瀨埋尿先分啦"},{"pid":"98778f1382cbdd2fbeef4d58b59b01a2ae193c1d","tid":966032,"uid":224862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e7772f7e90c701d8b433971de8e0b938f633fc6","tid":966032,"uid":194076,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:24:08.000Z","msg":"瀨埋尿先分啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"陣屎味真係頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080cb33b8b6007628d4bbc1112326ab22d9c6b7b","tid":966032,"uid":78166,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:26:13.000Z","msg":"樓主玩到條仔個菊花鬆哂重好意思同人分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35cc5aabbbd8feb10aa69cd1a9fc15a5946c454f","tid":966032,"uid":162783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:28:05.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"fa249ebd35025e2a802c5de3c04e5af7e047f812","tid":966032,"u